    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in fair condition. The interior shows visible wear on upholstery and trim, including staining and scuffing in high-contact areas. Controls and displays are functional. The exterior has noticeable scratches and minor dents consistent with regular use. Mechanically operational with no major issues reported, but the overall condition reflects typical wear beyond normal use.",
      "price": 17500.0,
